track_notes: Longer but less touristic route than from the Muttersbergbahn cable car station. Most parts of the steep track can be bypassed on the forest road. Free parking at starting point.
Taking the gondola saves a considerable amount of time.
track_title: Ascent from gondola top station Muttersberg
